{"type": "article", "id": 31159, "title": "新加坡有个李白餐厅，它新开的小吃店设计也很有趣", "description": "柔柔淡淡给人很舒服的视觉体验。", "date": "2016-08-18T04:59:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 10665, "name": "品牌设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 336, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160818123453k4C3NABbsKRLwayE.jpg", "contents": "<p>在新加坡喜来登酒店，以诗仙李白命名的主题餐厅，是新加坡中式餐厅中的标杆，开业已超过 30 年。广式点心是其招牌，品种虽然算不上包罗万象，但招牌的原盅鸡汤、调味猪排配炸馒头和虾仁扇贝酿豆腐等，据说都是必尝菜点。</p><p>最近，李白餐厅在新加坡又尝试新开了一家广东特色小吃餐厅 Full of Luck Club 福乐，鱼子鸡肉烧卖、香芒炸虾筒、脆皮叉烧酥以及酱炒萝卜糕等都是经典广式小吃，除此之外，还将提供一些中式风味的沙拉以及精酿啤酒等等。</p><p>为了帮助这个新品牌尽快建立辨识度，Full of Luck Club 福乐找来了在纽约、新加坡两地办公的<a href=\"http://bravo.rocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计工作室 Bravo</a>。这是一个专门从事品牌设计的创意工作室，过往的设计案例都是比较大胆的艺术路线，服务过包括科技、食品、饮料行业在内的不少品牌。</p><p>在 Full of Luck Club 福乐这个案例中，从名字便不难看出，业主是想要传递出一种随时随地伴随在身边的好运的概念。而相较于诸品牌李白餐厅，定价较为亲民的 Full of Luck Club 福乐也希望能够占领更多年轻人的市场，所以它需要一个有趣、充满活力且令人难忘的品牌形象。</p><p>Bravo 的做法还是从色彩出发。不管是蓝色勾边的白色线条、红白条纹的丝带元素还是蓝纹绕圈的白色管状元素，都是以肆意弯曲蔓延开来的形式在纯色的名片纸上铺开，有一种青春张扬的意味在里面，各种暖调的奶油色系铺底，搭配烫金字体的品牌名称，衬托出一种精致感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818123824I1oinJ3cauGrFb8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608181238240rkU7zSmsHXgOFpt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818123825ldBHw9pJ053v1CIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818123826ojtVTRfPrAOBxbSk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818123826RFft0UkEGNv9aW6x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608181238265wAsGXotJqm2PZkU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>纸质菜单的配色也很清新，比如用浅粉色菜单纸搭配紫色字体，淡黄色菜单纸搭配蓝色字体，以及天蓝色菜单纸搭配玫红色字体，柔柔淡淡给人很舒服的视觉体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818123850mIMtaAS2Tbj14zsv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608181238506SxPXKArfwyjUTsn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124017EvhndVofxyKSZHjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124018DqLMXrSz2h5Qct63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>当然，Bravo 团队的很多作品都给人类似这种年轻化的体验。</p><p>比如为美国披萨品牌 ALT. 设计的披萨盒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124039WZ1x4g7utLibw9OC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.890588\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124121Hk8wE4nxO62VuRpm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.401500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>比如为生活方式精品店 Beauty Candy 设计的包装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124153SwRMfhPDkU21b4FX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667059\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124154d869WquYeaMmLrHD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124154v5092zJaUNYSXfrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>以及为雅加达一家意大利餐厅 Sopra Cucina &amp; Bar 做的全套包装设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124221zqKmMAYugd6VyoHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124221gw3nNaPrM1ql49vs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160818124222Ez1jGWKAHQICsyMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/full-of-luck-club-tasty-branding-by-bravo-for-a-modern-cantonese-kitchen/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creative Boom</a>、<a href=\"http://bravo.rocks/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bravo</a></p>"}